幾多日有結果?"},{"pid":"60d428d85de98edf13e94191d610cc84749ffe02","tid":2500690,"uid":59481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"戒j"},{"pid":"8fc26cbe2bb7db4a140d79bb7761d740d9490e49","tid":2500690,"uid":289396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"通常抽血+ 驗尿係咪基本包哂check 到所有大病"},{"pid":"c6ee923217f141373b279b2ef532fcc554caa58c","tid":2500690,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"肺炎, 去狗屋.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15041bfd746eaadb4b7f5b101fba8e0de11f334b","tid":2500690,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce9981c2429f6cb78b4647172c472564e58a8008","tid":2500690,"uid":201449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"拿拿臨睇醫生啦<br />\n肺朥, cancer, hormonal changes都有可能<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.webmd.com/menopause/guide/8-causes-of-night-sweats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Fmenopause%2Fguide%2F8-causes-of-night-sweats&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=bb9c0148\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.webmd.com/menopause/guide/8-causes-of-night-sweats</a><br />\n1. Infections. Tuberculosis is the infection most commonly associated with night sweats. But bacterial infections, such as endocarditis (inflammation of the heart valves), osteomyelitis (inflammation in the bones), and abscesses can cause night sweats. Night sweats are also a symptom of HIV infection.<br />\n2. Cancers. Night sweats are an early symptom of some cancers. The most common type of cancer associated with night sweats is lymphoma. However, people who have an undiagnosed cancer frequently have other symptoms as well, such as unexplained weight loss and fevers.<br />\n3. Hormone disorders. Sweating or flushing can be seen with several hormone disorders, including pheochromocytoma, carcinoid syndrome, and hyperthyroidism."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXdBnzFRaWhsy22N62WbJpnLC1dRaN4dDbm1zifYax65V?filename=pWQZUO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWQZUO6.jpg&h=eb537e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bff7e7d7dce45c2e65da2b2aa9fbc5121449bf6","tid":2500690,"uid":278265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"我之前有一排都係咁 可能壓力太大加上訓得唔好<br />\n後尾成日花旗參片煲水飲 同埋keep住食milk thistle(本身諗住用嚟護肝)先好返 不過我唔係醫生 唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"89ce19b37249d8530e19269d3b890290cc61c97c","tid":2500690,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"中醫真係睇運氣<br />\n睇左3-4次都冇效就直接換另一個<br />\n唔好晒時間"},{"pid":"20030065500f883109f43be02f22b63fe9385279","tid":2500690,"uid":289396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89ce19b37249d8530e19269d3b890290cc61c97c","tid":2500690,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"中醫真係睇運氣<br />\n睇左3-4次都冇效就直接換另一個<br />\n唔好晒時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"三四次 都算俾得多機會"},{"pid":"d289286d51712dcfe82854cae023279d449327d3","tid":2500690,"uid":289396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bff7e7d7dce45c2e65da2b2aa9fbc5121449bf6","tid":2500690,"uid":278265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"我之前有一排都係咁 可能壓力太大加上訓得唔好<br />\n後尾成日花旗參片煲水飲 同埋keep住食milk thistle(本身諗住用嚟護肝)先好返 不過我唔係醫生 唔知關唔關事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"就咁沖滾水定要煲"},{"pid":"744bbbc9a907297857e9cc091bd1b2dca59131ed","tid":2500690,"uid":278265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d289286d51712dcfe82854cae023279d449327d3","tid":2500690,"uid":289396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bff7e7d7dce45c2e65da2b2aa9fbc5121449bf6","tid":2500690,"uid":278265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl