sweats\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Fmenopause%2Fguide%2F8-causes-of-night-sweats&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=bb9c0148\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.webmd.com/menopause/guide/8-causes-of-night-sweats</a><br />\n1. Infections. Tuberculosis is the infection most commonly associated with night sweats. But bacterial infections, such as endocarditis (inflammation of the heart valves), osteomyelitis (inflammation in the bones), and abscesses can cause night sweats. Night sweats are also a symptom of HIV infection.<br />\n2. Cancers. Night sweats are an early symptom of some cancers. The most common type of cancer associated with night sweats is lymphoma. However, people who have an undiagnosed cancer frequently have other symptoms as well, such as unexplained weight loss and fevers.<br />\n3. Hormone disorders. Sweating or flushing can be seen with several hormone disorders, including pheochromocytoma, carcinoid syndrome, and hyperthyroidism."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWQZUO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWQZUO6.jpg&h=eb537e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑左"},{"pid":"1be05ca02b01a1be3c31d08e1c1f91725d06f27c","tid":2500690,"uid":119017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77eda24f5f9fe2fdde48b4d66c4e4659ccc48706","tid":2500690,"uid":119017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:53:54.000Z","msg":"如果一直都係咁，又無話有其他唔舒服就似氣虛<br />\n我另一半都係咁<br />\n我焗麥冬、浮小麥茶佢飲<br />\n有改善<br />\n<br />\n最好睇睇中醫調理，怕貴的話中醫車好平<br />\n幾十蚊劑藥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"sorry唔係氣虛，係個人虛"},{"pid":"6c9bed07b9a74da00fd09aab6940cab313987faf","tid":2500690,"uid":289396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1be05ca02b01a1be3c31d08e1c1f91725d06f27